{"tid":786936,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ iPad 電池爆炸　Apple 阿姆斯特丹分店需暫時關閉","createTime":"2018-08-20T09:38:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T05:43:53.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ef0c24fb48a75864b5a8adaad5942db80c352759","tid":786936,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:38:59.000Z","msg":"最近蘋果在阿姆斯特丹的分店發生 iPad 電池爆炸，由於擔心顧客與員工吸入對人體有害的化學物質，店內人士需要緊急疏散，分店需要暫時關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據外媒《iCulture》報道，在爆炸後，蘋果工作人員把電池移往裝滿沙的容器內。可幸的是，爆炸沒有引致起火，事件中沒人受傷。但三名員工表示呼吸困難，已接受救援人員治療。由於爆炸可能會釋出有害物質，店內的人需疏散，而分店需暫時關閉，好讓消防人員排走氣體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/08/20/ipadbatteryexplosioncausedclosedownofapplestore/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F08%2F20%2Fipadbatteryexplosioncausedclosedownofapplestore%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=LaYFzeWo0jmsFzezrbAsBwIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=c2255ed8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/08/20/ipadbatteryexplosioncausedclosedownofapplestore/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"df5a668c1b3024b788a9c0637f6c63daca0d95c0","tid":786936,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef2b85e4734988cd6b338484d60c48a15ba75f63","tid":786936,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"apple rip"},{"pid":"511f08fa3ee9b9ef1eec3d4b9d5c873dce048b11","tid":786936,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-20T09:40:05.000Z","msg":"等睇班idog點駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11235cca17c20675c452f1fb06fec90dc8253914","tid":786936,"uid":183991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score"